  "detailed_description": "<h1>New DLC Available</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633260/extras/ac32667242027bcdaf8c2d00db9e380c.avif?t=1665723448\" width=300 height=126 /></span><br>Sicko Island - Rex Pack is the newest addition to the game.<br>It includes a new companion that can alert you for incoming spiders, defend against enemies, find hidden objects and even play fetch with you.</p><br><h1>New DLC Available</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633260/extras/5ccf548d3159b1b04221242790b5ccde.avif?t=1665723448\" width=300 height=126 /></span><br>Sicko Island - Halloween Pack is the second addition to the game.<br>It includes a new trading system, new items to collect, new enemies, new damage type, and plenty more...</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SICKO ISLAND</strong></h2><br>On a dark and stormy night, your boat crashes on a strange Island.<br>Stranded, you soon discover this is no ordinary Island.<br>It's controlled by a crazed General who, in his secret lab, creating a special serum and testing it on his least worthy soldiers.<br>His goal is to finally get his formula right and create a super soldier.<br>In order to escape the Island, you must find essential items, solve puzzles and fight your way to the General.<br>Can you survive the night on SICKO ISLAND ?",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SICKO ISLAND</strong></h2><br>On a dark and stormy night, your boat crashes on a strange Island.<br>Stranded, you soon discover this is no ordinary Island.<br>It's controlled by a crazed General who, in his secret lab, creating a special serum and testing it on his least worthy soldiers.<br>His goal is to finally get his formula right and create a super soldier.<br>In order to escape the Island, you must find essential items, solve puzzles and fight your way to the General.<br>Can you survive the night on SICKO ISLAND ?",
